  "governance_notes": "All children preserve Stage1 and Stage2 fields. ParseCommand and TrackOrder are pure functions (no side effects). PlaceOrder and CancelOrder are atomic operations with read_write access to orders, inventory, and payments. global_vars and data_operations are synchronized exactly with internal_leaf_accesses. Constraints and acceptance criteria derived from functional requirements and pre/postconditions.",
